<h2 id="get-ready-with-the-latest-beta-releases">Get ready with the latest beta releases
</h2><p>May 26, 2026</p>
<p>The beta versions of iOS 26.6, iPadOS 26.6, macOS 26.6, tvOS 26.6, visionOS 26.6, and watchOS 26.6 are now available. Get your apps ready by confirming they work as expected on these releases. And make sure to build and test with Xcode 26.5 to take advantage of the advancements in the latest SDKs.</p>
